lyrics:
[Verse]
Pricilla, she's a Brazilian queen
With a smile that's brighter than sunbeams (ooh-yeah)
She dances through the streets, so carefree
Her dog Kobe, always there by her side (by her side)
They make a team, a love that's so pure

[Chorus]
Pricilla and Kobe, a bond that can't be broken (can't be broken)
Through all the ups and the downs, they're never losin'
They're chasin' dreams, catchin' every moment (oh-oh-oh)
Pricilla and Kobe, love in motion (love in motion)
Oh-oh-oh-oh-oh-oh-oh
Oh-oh-oh-oh-oh-oh-oh
